# This file is used locally by Vite to map your custom variables.
# When you deploy to Vercel, you will add this exact same variable inside 
# Vercel's "Environment Variables" settings tab, pointing to your real Render URL!

# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://leadgensite-backend.onrender.com

# For local development, you can leave this blank or commented out, 
# and it will default back to http://localhost:5000 automatically.
